data.description: This is a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath home located in Normandy Isles. The beautiful house features a living room, formal dining room, entertainment room, breakfast nook, and two huge walk-in closets in the master bedroom. The house has tile flooring throughout, a bar near the dining room, and is excellent for family gatherings with its extended patio, sizable backyard, and a spectacular lake view. The property boasts well-maintained fruit trees, a new energy-efficient gas water heater, and dryer. Additionally, it has the lowest HOA fees in the area, coming in at an affordable $47 per month.
